  "requestedIntent": "Turn ACEF's control-pricing rationale into a machine-readable lane/control dosing manifest with validator, lane-closeout consumer, dose-sensitive lean-evidence behavior, and installer support, so agents cannot silently rewrite which controls are required for quick-fix, lightweight, guarded, and full-BMAD lanes.",
